    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/83f0c487ab83b50383615d3ae174657e.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/392bda1b75baba9dfd3a7c1cbff06e2f.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/392bda1b75baba9dfd3a7c1cbff06e2f.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>为客户建造迷你房屋：打造独特而舒适的可移动小房子。定制每个房屋以反映客户的偏好，同时融入您个人的风格。从乡村小屋到简约的现代设计，可能性无穷无尽！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/ea1c8f1a95a54f0fd59c28362e4f54fe.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/1dd2f6f5e9d2d49d9e0dd1253de79749.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/1dd2f6f5e9d2d49d9e0dd1253de79749.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>踏上冒险之旅，穿越一个生动多样的岛屿，每一个角落都藏着新的惊喜。探索位于西海岸的热闹小镇，在岛屿中央的宁静湖泊旁放松，或者前往东南部的群山。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/839e7adb43fd039951467597303d25b8.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/9f17644b8bb617b153167e028e663d75.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/9f17644b8bb617b153167e028e663d75.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>掌控您如何经营业务、设计迷你房屋，并在Tiny Island上自由漫游。开放世界的游戏玩法为您提供无尽的机会和体验，完美契合您的个性风格。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/51c46ff2350d044bb885c5b793e75803.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/cfe902188e749e87a1c3f14eb524e8e9.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/cfe902188e749e87a1c3f14eb524e8e9.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>将您的作品连接到可靠的车辆上，并将它们送到岛上的满意客户手中。在蜿蜒的道路上、风景优美的路线以及具有挑战性的地形中前行，直达目标。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/7fa1c4da380ec918286b6eda2185e70e.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/9e54439ec1b2a7731a6db528e5f08a56.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/9e54439ec1b2a7731a6db528e5f08a56.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>管理和扩展您的迷你房屋业务。利用辛苦赚来的收入来改善您的工作坊，投资更好的车辆，或者在当地赌场碰碰运气。努力创造更大更令人印象深刻的房屋！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/468bd07080061353ca585a18df7bdaf8.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/5947fa6356bf2f5f3d13aafcd251776c.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/5947fa6356bf2f5f3d13aafcd251776c.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>欣赏壮观的风景和地标，包括节庆区域、山丘上的风车以及小岛上的灯塔。在沙滩上放松或者探索位于西南的热闹机场。<br><br>您准备好迎接终极迷你房屋挑战了吗？开始这段温馨的旅程，将您的小规模梦想变成繁荣的事业！  <br>今天就在Steam上获取Tiny House Simulator，开始打造您的梦想家园！",
